# PFE: Customer Lifetime Value, Segmentation & Recommendation System

## Overview

Build a complete data science project for Dislog Group combining **Subject 2** (Customer Lifetime Value & Segmentation) with **Subject 6** (Market Basket Analysis & Recommendations) as a bonus chapter.

**Data**: ~1GB of raw CSV files from Dislog (Region, Sector, Customer, Seller, Product, SalesHeader, SalesLine, Invoice).

**Timeline**: 5-6 months (Feb → Jul/Aug 2026).

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Choice**: The provided [Schema.sql](file:///c:/Users/21261/Desktop/dislog-pfe/Schema.sql) targets SQL Server. Do you have SQL Server installed, or should we use **PostgreSQL** or **SQLite** instead? This affects the ETL pipeline setup.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dashboard Tool**: Do you prefer **Power BI** (more corporate/polished) or **Streamlit** (Python-based, easier to code, interactive web app)? We can do both, but I'd like to know your priority.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Python Environment**: Do you want to use a virtual environment (`venv`) or **conda**? I see a `.venv` folder already exists.

