## Project Structure

```
dislog-pfe/
├── Data/                          # Raw CSV files (already present)
├── notebooks/                     # Jupyter notebooks for each phase
│   ├── 01_data_profiling.ipynb
│   ├── 02_eda.ipynb
│   ├── 03_rfm_analysis.ipynb
│   ├── 04_segmentation.ipynb
│   ├── 05_churn_prediction.ipynb
│   ├── 06_clv_model.ipynb
│   └── 07_market_basket.ipynb
├── src/                           # Reusable Python modules
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── config.py                  # DB connection, file paths, constants
│   ├── etl/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── extract.py             # Read CSVs with encoding handling
│   │   ├── transform.py           # Clean, deduplicate, type casting
│   │   └── load.py                # Load into SQL database
│   ├── features/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── rfm.py                 # RFM feature engineering
│   │   └── clv.py                 # CLV calculation
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── segmentation.py        # K-Means, DBSCAN clustering
│   │   ├── churn.py               # Churn prediction (XGBoost/RF)
│   │   └── recommender.py         # Market basket & recommendations
│   └── viz/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       └── plots.py               # Reusable plotting functions
├── dashboard/                     # Streamlit or Power BI files
├── reports/                       # Final PFE report, slides
├── Schema.sql                     # Database schema (already present)
├── requirements.txt               # Python dependencies
├── README.MD                      # Project README (already present)
└── .gitignore
```

