---

### Phase 5: Bonus — Recommendation System (Month 4-5)

---

#### [NEW] [src/models/recommender.py](file:///c:/Users/21261/Desktop/dislog-pfe/src/models/recommender.py)

Market basket & recommendations:
- **Association rules**: Apriori algorithm on SalesLine data (product co-purchases per order)
  - Use sampling or FP-Growth to handle the 719MB file efficiently
  - Calculate support, confidence, lift
- **Collaborative filtering**: User-item matrix → cosine similarity
  - "Customers who bought X also bought Y"
- Integration with customer segments: different recommendations per segment

---

#### [NEW] [notebooks/07_market_basket.ipynb](file:///c:/Users/21261/Desktop/dislog-pfe/notebooks/07_market_basket.ipynb)

- Run Apriori on sampled transaction data
- Display top association rules
- Network graph of product relationships
- Generate sample recommendations for specific customers

